{"type":null,"faqId":32835,"title":"如何将拍摄的照片和录像默认保存在microSD卡上？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>进入相机取景界面，点击右上角的菜单按钮，然后点击“设置”，设置“优先存储位置”为“SD 卡”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>手机在插入 microSD 卡后，拍摄的照片和录像会默认保存在 microSD 卡上，无需手动设置。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7537","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748419000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":22,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"照片,录像,默认保存,SD卡","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}